{"tid":2142899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[超長警世文] 習近平的監控帝國即將降臨","createTime":"2020-08-06T18:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T14:48:56.000Z","uid":83713,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b23992fe85894d1a08d55eaa07920d16d44fa9c6","tid":2142899,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:02:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2020/09/china-ai-surveillance/614197/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fmagazine%2Farchive%2F2020%2F09%2Fchina-ai-surveillance%2F614197%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOliy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=11220db0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2020/09/china-ai-surveillance/614197/</a><br />\n<br />\n係twitter見到呢篇超長文，我知實在太長、好難入口，但都想放上嚟分享下<br />\n<br />\n內容大致係分析習近平點樣利用AI同監控技術，一步一步建立佢嘅監控帝國。裏面提到新疆只係習近平嘅實驗室，而習近平正利用武漢肺炎同輸出技術到專制國家+強制分享資料，進一步擴充佢嘅數據資料庫。個計劃已經開始左，作者話根據現有速度推算，支共嘅AI科技會係2030年超越美國。<br />\n<br />\n大家可能覺得支共吹水姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊有可能爬到美帝頭。但入面提到支那已經發展緊讀心(其實係測腦電波)術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前大家成日講嘅信用評級制度只係頭盤，中共最後嘅目標係建立一套可以監察埋思想嘅監控制度，同佢啲&rdquo;盟友&rdquo;一齊使用。由於支那相對佢班廢物盟友嘅技術水平係超班，可以預期佢將會成為對抗自由世界嘅領頭羊。假如乜都唔做嘅話，篇文預測支共係有能力響未來壓制到美國嘅核攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面都有提侵侵呢排對中國起哂槓，踢走哂班響美國讀書嘅支那學生，某程度上係壓住左支共個勢，而事實上未來10年都仲會係美帝主宰AI。我自己都唔信美帝會容許支那軍事實力超越自己。<br />\n<br />\n但問題係假如China Joe贏左，到時中門大開會至少令美帝失去4年時間，而支共利用呢4年傾盡全國之力發展AI又真係有進步的話，去到2030年鹿死誰手就未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完篇文好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />首先美帝班後生沉迷抖陰已經夠令人擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一諗起如果11月拜登贏左的話，篇文入面講嘅惡夢就會一步一步成真。個作者仲要膠膠地話只有支那人可以stop到習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哂鳩氣啦<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打講下除左打爆支共，仲有乜方法破到佢套監控系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者有證據話套系統其實不外如是都好丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9203c990798605f34b2372d03e649bf8c7d3e9d","tid":2142899,"uid":139173,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:04:03.000Z","msg":"如果唔使講人權<br />\n咁所有人都係農場入面既生產單位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe51ba98d6f9907a96d691d05f95ac04fbd3c260","tid":2142899,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5e373cfc0badc7e395d325774a06f8ae084d99","tid":2142899,"uid":83713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9203c990798605f34b2372d03e649bf8c7d3e9d","tid":2142899,"uid":139173,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:04:03.000Z","msg":"如果唔使講人權<br />\n咁所有人都係農場入面既生產單位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:10:53.000Z","msg":"作者有講，監控帝國呢樣野一定唔會係美國，以至重視人權嘅自由世界出現<br />\n但支共呢一刻偏偏有齊發展呢種技術嘅土壤同條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋支共隻政體係會令AI技術向住最差，即係完全漠視人性呢個方向發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢期武肺肆虐，只會令 &ldquo;交出個人資料就保你健康&rdquo;呢個narrative 更有市場"},{"pid":"1af56b3856c813484e375c725a5640a914b78251","tid":2142899,"uid":8918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:17:52.000Z","msg":"離少少題<br />\n你句：監察埋思想嘅監控制度<br />\n<br />\n最近我睇到  來自2060年 KFK 既文章<br />\n入面都有講到 人心赤露 要善良既人同有好既品質先會有比較好既出路<br />\n唔知會唔會有一絲關連"},{"pid":"f655da872fb82be474c2e7f874d717652589cc88","tid":2142899,"uid":83713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1af56b3856c813484e375c725a5640a914b78251","tid":2142899,"uid":8918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:17:52.000Z","msg":"離少少題<br />\n你句：監察埋思想嘅監控制度<br />\n<br />\n最近我睇到  來自2060年 KFK 既文章<br />\n入面都有講到 人心赤露 要善良既人同有好既品質先會有比較好既出路<br />\n唔知會唔會有一絲關連"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:24:33.000Z","msg":"入面有訪問一個教AI Ethics既大陸人<br />\n作者問佢如果第時整到一個智能上超越左人類、唯獨是未有同理心嘅機械人，而支共迫佢交個機械人出嚟，佢會點做<br />\n個大陸人話佢會即刻拆左個機械人之後匿埋。<br />\n我當佢係發自內心講呢句，但大佬呀實際上邊有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a06032903eddfe99d948691b62a2bd19cd8e1e6","tid":2142899,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152c3f5710058a73c7e00e0c0a4bbff0108e745c","tid":2142899,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:50:21.000Z","msg":"科技比仆街控制真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de3139eda76b2eca55a71b84023af288006c024","tid":2142899,"uid":161684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T19:38:12.000Z","msg":"所以點解係時代革命<br />\n呢場係廿一世紀嘅希波戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3cbdbd71b45706395